      "rawText": "3:54Danube [253898724]UploadHyperpop and glitchcore track at 160 BPM in G major, The arrangement features high-pitched, chipmunk-style female vocals with heavy pitch correction and formant shifting, A distorted, overdriven 808 bass provides the melodic and rhythmic core, playing syncopated patterns, The percussion consists of sharp, metallic snares, rapid-fire hi-hat rolls, and glitchy foley samples, A bright, detuned sawtooth synth lead plays a repetitive, staccato melody, Frequent use of bitcrushing, stutter edits, and sudden silence creates a fragmented texture, The track incorporates spoken word samples from a cartoon or anime, processed with a telephone filter, A secondary synth layer uses a square wave with a fast LFO on the filter cutoff for a wobbling effect2PublishRemix",
